{"tid":1687483,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[安全情報］警方於中西、灣仔區的「布袋陣」戰略 （附地圖）","createTime":"2019-11-02T01:12:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-02T01:58:12.000Z","uid":48083,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"1403c5a65e0a6ad8604bfff3950727949f9d10a8","tid":1687483,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T01:12:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/11/02/091037_5354619b0efb4c33cec1cec8c911f23b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F11%2F02%2F091037_5354619b0efb4c33cec1cec8c911f23b.png&h=455f4113&s={SIZE}\" />虎頭鍘製作 FU Production<br />\n<br />\n聽日大家小心。<br />\n<br />\nfrom tg:<br />\n<br />\n#公眾安全情報 #民防安全地圖 #金鐘<br />\n<br />\n警方於中西、灣仔區的「布袋陣」戰略<br />\n<br />\n中西、灣仔區近一個月沒有嚴重衝突，氣象巴打與大家重溫警方的「布袋陣」：<br />\n<br />\n⚠️金鐘出現衝突後，防暴會於灣仔電腦城天橋及修頓球場附近設防，阻止民眾繼續前進；<br />\n⚠️與此同時，防暴會由中環交易廣場附近向金鐘推進，同樣是阻止民眾繼續前進；<br />\n⚠️假如政總附近發生衝突，防暴會衝出夏慤道並將民眾推至金鐘道，期間會作第一輪拘捕行動；<br />\n⚠️防暴會再沿金鐘道推進，務求民眾經軒尼詩道或皇后大道東折返灣仔，期間會作第二輪拘捕行動；<br />\n⚠️防暴會於警總天橋戒備，但包圍次序一般屬最後。當防暴大致封鎖金鐘後，警總天橋的防暴才會向灣仔推進，但民眾撤退期間會發射催淚彈；<br />\n⚠️民眾開始由金鐘撤退後，防暴會沿菲林明道進入灣仔，發射催淚彈並開始該區的驅散行動。<br />\n<br />\n‼️警方對中西、灣仔區的驅散戰略可謂非常熟練。民眾務必密切留意各哨兵頻道，預早安排多於一條撤離路線，避免憑直覺逃至自以為安全的地方（特別適用於沿皇后大道東撤退的民眾）。"},{"pid":"2095bc18aa863cbc5c1047c0b41203fa1c5f98c0","tid":1687483,"uid":33498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T01:20:29.000Z","msg":"甴曱平"},{"pid":"3bc980644bacd4b277ddbf443af18a2be9f00a7b","tid":1687483,"uid":12824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T01:21:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8606d8f0dc6b9a96d48e623125d4239a6e124ea6","tid":1687483,"uid":199012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T01:22:11.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"00af87078e7add427db944e55e4386b9cb13a204","tid":1687483,"uid":245713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T01:22:13.000Z","msg":"習曱甴"},{"pid":"c6086cfcbc12132985395a098baa258d45abdfda","tid":1687483,"uid":199012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T01:22:21.000Z","msg":"有用"},{"pid":"b933159f2e26cffa2204af36b459dd58d32f30d4","tid":1687483,"uid":199012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T01:22:45.000Z","msg":"習曱甴"},{"pid":"4fe086f8a29e4327acd1475f58d6a30536b5781b","tid":1687483,"uid":110509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T01:40:04.000Z","msg":"無落雨都好<br />\n<br />\n帶直遮帶水"},{"pid":"ae5d726a4d85ad61243f97edbc7bbe608f27b6ec","tid":1687483,"uid":110509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T01:40:57.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"6e257154e24e75ede16fac95110cbb4d8a7b297b","tid":1687483,"uid":110509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T01:41:44.000Z","msg":"必要時上山再落中環<br />\n當然睇情況，小心有狗伏"},{"pid":"3cd8811454cd9d78c5d289af153a25f36fdf6bef","tid":1687483,"uid":91205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T01:42:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53be9738eede9a2d52f139a5dcb782f64acbb0b2","tid":1687483,"uid":268541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T01:43:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7dbb097992063b8d230f0b5dad7070af96dbbb48","tid":1687483,"uid":19634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T01:47:18.000Z","msg":"有用post唔好畀佢沉，不過勁多mon po狗所以好有可能改變策略，盡量唔好留一個地方太耐畀對面慢慢部署，而且又有直昇機，只能隨機應變，萬事小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b407bb50ff193ce03512e5da2c4323489b9eaa4","tid":1687483,"uid":19634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7dbb097992063b8d230f0b5dad7070af96dbbb48","tid":1687483,"uid":19634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T01:47:18.000Z","msg":"有用post唔好畀佢沉，不過勁多mon po